#MEM id=rules source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/mia/skills/design-and-build/vercel-react-best-practices/rules/rendering-usetransition-loading.md
M|rules|title: Use useTransition Over Manual Loading States
M|rules|impact: LOW
M|rules|impactDescription: reduces re-renders and improves code clarity
M|rules|tags: rendering, transitions, useTransition, loading, state
M|rules|Use `useTransition` instead of manual `useState` for loading states. This provides built-in `isPending` state and automatically manages transitions.
M|rules|**Incorrect (manual loading state):**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|function SearchResults() {
M|rules|const [query, setQuery] = useState('')
M|rules|const [results, setResults] = useState([])
M|rules|const [isLoading, setIsLoading] = useState(false)
M|rules|const handleSearch = async (value: string) => {
M|rules|setIsLoading(true)
M|rules|setQuery(value)
M|rules|const data = await fetchResults(value)
M|rules|setResults(data)
M|rules|setIsLoading(false)
M|rules|}
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<>
M|rules|<input onChange={(e) => handleSearch(e.target.value)} />
M|rules|{isLoading && <Spinner />}
M|rules|<ResultsList results={results} />
M|rules|</>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Correct (useTransition with built-in pending state):**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|import { useTransition, useState } from 'react'
M|rules|function SearchResults() {
M|rules|const [query, setQuery] = useState('')
M|rules|const [results, setResults] = useState([])
M|rules|const [isPending, startTransition] = useTransition()
M|rules|const handleSearch = (value: string) => {
M|rules|setQuery(value) // Update input immediately
M|rules|startTransition(async () => {
M|rules|// Fetch and update results
M|rules|const data = await fetchResults(value)
M|rules|setResults(data)
M|rules|})
M|rules|}
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<>
M|rules|<input onChange={(e) => handleSearch(e.target.value)} />
M|rules|{isPending && <Spinner />}
M|rules|<ResultsList results={results} />
M|rules|</>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Benefits:**
M|rules|- **Automatic pending state**: No need to manually manage `setIsLoading(true/false)`
M|rules|- **Error resilience**: Pending state correctly resets even if the transition throws
M|rules|- **Better responsiveness**: Keeps the UI responsive during updates
M|rules|- **Interrupt handling**: New transitions automatically cancel pending ones
M|rules|Reference: [useTransition](https://react.dev/reference/react/useTransition)